TITLE: 5/3/1: The Simplest and Most Effective Training System for Raw Strength (2nd Edition)
AUTHOR: Jim Wendler
YEAR: 2009 - 2011
LANGUAGE: English
FORMAT: PDF

SYNOPSIS: The success of the 5/3/1 Method has been nothing short of extraordinary. For the 3 years, the response towards this simple but brutally effective training system has been overwhelming. This is because it works. And works for just about anyone willing to put in the discipline and work that getting stronger requires.
